name: Craigdarroch Archway
description:
The entryway arches of Craigdarroch Castle, in Victoria, British Columbia. Step through them and into the rich history of this stately Canadian home.

"Inviting You Through" series, #0.

Gifted to all who Collected my photos in 2021, as a thank you for collecting, and a teaser for my next "Inviting You Through" series. It will include windows and covered passages, which will invite you to look or travel through them, to see what's on the other side, or simply enjoy the journey of getting there.
